# otherItemsProxy

**Type Property**

The identifier of the special “other items proxy”, which is used to nest bars up the responder chain.

## Declaration

```swift
static let otherItemsProxy: NSTouchBarItem.Identifier
```

## Discussion

Use this identifier in the [doc://com.apple.appkit/documentation/AppKit/NSTouchBar/itemIdentifiers] array of an [doc://com.apple.appkit/documentation/AppKit/NSTouchBar] object, and a special proxy item will be instantiated for you.

When the [doc://com.apple.appkit/documentation/AppKit/NSTouchBar] containing this item is visible, bars provided by objects closer to the first responder will be nested inside the space denoted for this item.Note that a touch bar lacking this item identifier will be replaced in its entirety by touch bars closer to the first responder in the responder chain.
